trans-unit.source: The PackagePartCollection class has no public constructor.
trans-unit.target: PackagePartCollection 类具有没有公共构造函数。

trans-unit.source: This class is created and returned by the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.GetParts%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
Returns an enumerator for iterating through the parts in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个枚举数循环访问集合中的部分。

trans-unit.source: The collection accessed by the enumerator is invalidated after any change occurs to the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 对基础集合发生任何更改后，会失效集合枚举器访问的集合。

trans-unit.source: The underlying collection can change when the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreatePart%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method or <xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.DeletePart%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method is called.
trans-unit.target: 该基础集合可以更改时<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreatePart%2A?displayProperty=fullName>方法或<xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.DeletePart%2A?displayProperty=fullName>调用方法。</xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.DeletePart%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.Package.CreatePart%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: An enumerator for iterating through the <xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"></xref> elements in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 循环访问的枚举数<xref href="System.IO.Packaging.PackagePart"></xref>集合中的元素。

trans-unit.source: For a description of this member, see <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable.GetEnumerator%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
trans-unit.target: 此成员是显式接口成员的实现。

trans-unit.source: It can be used only when the <xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePartCollection> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: 可以使用它时，才<xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePartCollection>实例被强制转换为<xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>接口。</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> </xref:System.IO.Packaging.PackagePartCollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> object that can be used to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>可用于循环访问集合的对象。</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>
